        <updateDate>2023-06-29T13:57:44Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Nuclear Waste Informed Consent Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the Department of Energy (DOE) from using the Nuclear Waste Fund for planning, constructing, or operating a repository of nuclear waste unless DOE has obtained consent from the state in which the repository is located, affected local governments, and Indian tribes.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
